race.comment: THE KILL CLUB (13) deserved her 56 win at Ararat as a $3.20 favourite and then stepped up to a 70 at Warrnambool against her own sex and was beaten a whisker from the speed. Carries 2kg more but is well-placed in a 62 and can bounce back.MY ANGEL SHELL (4) resumes and the speedy galloper has raced well in stronger than this. Has placed fresh and has jumped out well at Ararat. POLISHED WOOD (11) recorded a game win at Ararat on debut, racing three-wide without cover throughout. He will have taken fitness and learning and will run along from an inside barrier. Tougher but is sure to give a sight. HE'S GODSPEED (15) mixes the form, but she's up to this. Had an excuse at Donald last time in better grade, and Meech rides today and can use the rails gate to advantage. Has to be considered.
